What does the color green remind you of? Trees and leaves as well as the the grassland in summer? The color green commonly symbolizes hope, growth, energy and freshness. The color is thought to have calming effects due to its association with nature. In this video, CGTN Nature presents the beauty of the color green in its various shades. Check it out! The Colors of Nature This series combines music, color and natural scenery to give viewers a sensory experience. For more: Snowy Kanas in NW China's Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region The beauty of yellow sand The beauty of the color black The beauty of the color brown (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)